68
00:03:06,534 --> 00:03:09,258
vos zol ikh aykh dertseyln shvere tsaytn?

69
00:03:08,286 --> 00:03:11,469
efsher gedenkt ir nokh epes vos ir hot mir nisht dertseylt?

70
00:03:12,184 --> 00:03:19,068
